**[[Eligmidae|Eligmidae]] {{small|Gill, 1871}} †
**[[硨磲牡蠣科|硨磲牡蠣科]] [[Gryphaeidae|Gryphaeidae]] {{small|Vialov, 1936}}
**[[牡蠣科|牡蠣科]] [[Ostreidae|Ostreidae]] {{small|Rafinesque, 1815}}
*[[江珧蛤總科|江珧蛤總科]] [[Pinnoidea|Pinnoidea]] {{small|Leach, 1819}}
**[[江珧蛤科|江珧蛤科]] [[Pinnidae|Pinnidae]]
*Superfamily †[[Posidonioidea|Posidonioidea]] {{small|Neumayr, 1891}}
